* Handle nested stash types correctly
 - Specify the record schema type in the collection using nested types, for example:

   {
     "name": "string",
     "patient": {
       "height": uint64,
       "weight": uint64
     }
   }

 - Make sure the `stash_record` method returns the same shape

   {
     name: "Dan",
     patient: {
       height: 180,
       weight: 85
     }
   }

- Index definitions need to specify fields using JSON path syntax. e.g.

  field: "patient.height"
